    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《超级蚁群》是一款以昆虫世界为背景的殖民模拟策略游戏。你从拥有一个小蚁群开始，建立蚁穴，获取资源，清理地图上的区域，获得生存和发展。在这款沙盒游戏中，我们鼓励你创造自己独特的策略，并发现创造性的生存解决方案。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理蚁群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不能控制单个蚂蚁，只能对整个蚁群下达命令。你可以设定一个目标，成百上千的蚂蚁则能评估它们所在地区的情况，并自行选择行动的优先次序。你只需一次点击，就可以指挥整个由数百只蚂蚁组成的蚁群。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/9babbeebdc364002c1df2bd4aea7f07c.poster.avif?t=1759534149\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/9babbeebdc364002c1df2bd4aea7f07c.webm?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/9babbeebdc364002c1df2bd4aea7f07c.mp4?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义蚂蚁种类</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的蚁群是独一无二的。你可以饲养不同种类的蚂蚁，让它们专攻战斗、侦查、收割或其他职业。为了扩展并克服恶劣的环境，你需要构建并进化出具有特殊能力、独特外观和行为的新种群。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/4282add7ee24843be862e9a8e3d3046b.poster.avif?t=1759534149\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/4282add7ee24843be862e9a8e3d3046b.webm?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/4282add7ee24843be862e9a8e3d3046b.mp4?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >科技树</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基因树是你为你的蚁群寻找进化路径的地方。基因是植物和昆虫的关键遗传性状，是它们在特定环境中成功生存的关键。从飞行到织网，或者把蚜虫养成牲畜。你可以通过使用DNA点（一种特殊的游戏内资源，玩家可以通过完成任务、收割植物或打败其他昆虫来收集）来解锁它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/92ebde36393a397b1109518de7d8a936.poster.avif?t=1759534149\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/92ebde36393a397b1109518de7d8a936.webm?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/92ebde36393a397b1109518de7d8a936.mp4?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >盟友、威胁和敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将面对雨水、野火、资源匮乏和蚂蚁疾病等威胁。你将需要抵御瓢虫、蜘蛛、蝎子和其他大型掠食者等不速之客。你将对白蚁或黄蜂等其他社会性昆虫的敌对群落发动战争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/6b4e575c78188f9831d78885b23f3602.poster.avif?t=1759534149\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/6b4e575c78188f9831d78885b23f3602.webm?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/6b4e575c78188f9831d78885b23f3602.mp4?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开放式沙盒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有了程序生成的地图和新兴的生态系统，你每次重玩游戏都会有不同的体验。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >艺术风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富多彩的程式化3D艺术风格提供了一系列的情感体验——从可爱的小动物到严肃的捕食者。这有助于以一种有趣、吸引人和幽默的方式表现自然界的现实、规模和戏剧性。《超级蚁群》给人一种观看自然纪录片的感觉，并增加了插入、指导和参与这个微小世界的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/6761747fd42f59014cf14b9dee0e75a1.poster.avif?t=1759534149\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/6761747fd42f59014cf14b9dee0e75a1.webm?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815650/extras/6761747fd42f59014cf14b9dee0e75a1.mp4?t=1759534149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蚁群最后也是最重要的目标是在每个地方积累足够的资源，然后繁衍出新的蚁后，将来之不易的基因带到遥远的地方。通过完成这项任务，玩家将扩大他们的蚁穴网络，并向实现全球超级蚁群的目标更进一步。</p>",
